data.description: Fantastic opportunity to own this wonderfully maintained home in a quiet neighborhood! The large backyard, complete with a fire pit and backing to a greenbelt, is perfect for entertaining! As you walk in, you are welcomed by a spacious living room and a lovely kitchen featuring granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances! Beautiful water-resistant vinyl flooring! Bask in the natural light of the sunroom with a book and a cup of tea or morning coffee! The downstairs family room, which includes a cozy fireplace, is ideal for relaxing after a long day! The attached garage is sure to provide great convenience, especially during the cold winter months! Newer roof, paint job and upstairs carpet! Conveniently located near Terrace Park and only a stroll away from schools, dining and more! Easy access to I-70 and a short commute to Denver International Airport!
